  <help_text>If the valve were to close in the middle 
of equalizing the levels across the gate,
this would halt the normal operation.
Somewhat like being stuck in an elevator// Uncomment the following line to change the fontsize and font:
// fontsize=14
// fontfamily=SansSerif //possible: SansSerif,Serif,Monospaced


